OL,3,CScots soldiers continue wartime
OL,4,Ctradition with blanket design
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,FScottish soldiers have kept a wartime
OL,8,Ftradition going as they continued
OL,9,Ftheir annual blanket-decorating
OL,10,Fcompetition while deployed abroad.
OL,12,FSoldiers from 4th Battalion, the Royal
OL,13,FRegiment of Scotland (4Scots) have
OL,14,Fbeen based in Dhekelia, Cyprus, since
OL,15,FAugust.
OL,17,FIn the run-up to Christmas, they have
OL,18,Fbeen decorating blankets which are
OL,19,Fthen hung up for others in the
OL,20,Fbattalion to see, often reflecting on
OL,21,Fthe year gone by.
