OL,7,FThis year's competition saw another
OL,8,Fnoteworthy entry from last year's
OL,9,Fwinner, Corporal Lewis Devlin-May.
OL,11,FHis blanket depicts a stag standing
OL,12,Famong poppies, and is designed to
OL,13,Fremember those who came before.
OL,15,FMajor Jamie Mackinnon of 4Scots said:
OL,16,F"It's important to keep these
OL,17,Ftraditions going when you're at home,
OL,18,Fbut they matter even more when you're
OL,19,Fserving abroad.
