OL,3,CScots soldiers continue wartime
OL,4,Ctradition with blanket design
OL,5,Ccompetition
OL,7,F"They help keep the battalion
OL,8,Fconnected, remind the Jocks of home,
OL,9,Fboost morale, and it gives everyone a
OL,10,Fchance to pause and reflect on the
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,F"It's been a big year for us at
OL,14,F4Scots, and across the wider Royal
OL,15,FRegiment of Scotland, so the chance to
OL,16,Fcontinue a fun tradition and get
OL,17,Fcreative ahead of the festive period
OL,18,Fmeans a lot to the Jocks, even while
OL,19,Fthey remain focused on the job at
OL,20,Fhand."
